          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/81702-katy?shelf=childrens">childrens</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/81702-katy?shelf=middle-grade">middle-grade</a>, 
